| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1687 — Recovery Inhibition (apt73)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9c4cac5d-ee3c-51e4-b34f-b0db95f1be17"
